en.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-051/poem-1tip3669zaTHdgXEPv7hPg">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 051 - 山居百詠其五十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Thi%C3%AAn-sinh-v%E1%BA%A1n-t%E1%BB%AD-ph%C3%A0m-k%E1%BB%B7-sinh/poem-RQQzvbrCQ8IFAEuOyq0DoA">Thiên sinh vạn tử phàm kỷ sinh - 千生萬死凡幾生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-EGSnZ7N28FU5bpROlEk0dw">Thu dạ - 秋夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/V%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BA%A5t-n%C4%83ng-dung/poem-Sh5A2yL6ck69H1c3amSMlg">Vật bất năng dung - 物不能容</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
